TestAccountExecution_ExecuteSingle
└── given the Nexus account execution
    ├── when executing a single operation
    │   └── it should execute successfully and increment the counter
    ├── when executing a single operation that reverts
    │   └── it should revert and the counter should remain unchanged
    ├── when executing a single operation with a zero address
    │   └── it should revert and the counter should remain unchanged
    ├── when executing a single operation with empty calldata
    │   └── it should execute successfully with no changes
    ├── when executing a value transfer in a single operation
    │   └── it should transfer the correct amount of ETH to the receiver
    ├── when executing a token transfer in a single operation
    │   └── it should transfer the correct amount of tokens to the recipient
    └── when executing an approve and transferFrom operation
        └── it should approve and transfer the tokens correctly
